These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, tea, water, iced-tea
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, bus, car, jet-ski, roller
5 different games are played: whist, domino, monopoly, mah-jongg, bridge
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person playing bridge is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person playing domino is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person playing whist is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the person driving the bus is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the british##1
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person playing whist##1
11. the person driving the bus is the person playing whist##1
12. the person driving the car is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Beverage         | soy-milk  | 7up    | water | tea    | iced-tea  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Transport           | ship     | roller     | jet-ski  | bus   | car    |
| Game         | monopoly | mah-jongg    | domino | whist  | bridge |

