.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, golf, handball, snowboarding
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, rat, hamster, dog
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose, orchid, balloon-flower, iris
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is the owner of the horse##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the owner of the rat##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the person who's sport is parkour##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| Sport           | parkour   | golf | snowboarding    | handball | cycling |
| Pet   | rat | hamster     | dog | rabbit    | horse  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | rose | begonia    | iris      | orchid    |

