.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, green, yellow, white, blue
5 different games are played: snooker, go, mah-jongg, backgammon, chess
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball, climbing, swimming, rowing
 1. the person who likes white is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 2. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 3. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person playing go##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who likes grey##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Color         | green | blue | white  | yellow   | grey    |
| Game   | go        | chess | snooker | backgammon    | mah-jongg   |
| Sport     | tennis   | climbing | rowing      | volleyball | swimming |

