 3. the person playing poker is the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person playing snooker is the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
10. the person who likes light-blue is the person playing whist##1
11. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Color          | white        | emerald       | chestnut | blue   | light-blue  |
| Pet   | goat | dog | cat | turtle   | frog |
