The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, sailing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person playing canasta is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the ranch-style house##1
 3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the futuristic house is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person playing poker is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Pet          | frog    | bird  | guinea-pig | goat    | turtle      |
| House           | townhouse | ranch-style | futuristic  | craftsman | art-deco |
