 5. the teacher is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the coach is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the teacher##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the firefighter##1
12. the writer is the person who's sport is swimming##1
13. the firefighter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Birthday      | march      | june       | april         | october  | july |
| Job   | writer  | entrepreneur | coach | teacher  | firefighter  |
| Sport   | swimming    | tennis    | parkour        | water-polo | golf     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

