.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, sports, thriller, western
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, april, october, january, may
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, aconite, amaryllis, begonia
5 different games are played: domino, chess, monopoly, billiard, whist
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is the person playing domino##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
10. the person who growslily is the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1

