5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, rabbit, snake, dog
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing billiard is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person playing chess is the thai##1
